metadata.name: Unsupervised Data #421
metadata.description:
There is an invisible layer of our everyday reality made up of signals traveling through space. In taking the data that flows around us as the primary material and the flow of our life as a collaborator, I created **Unsupervised Data**

This artwork reflects on the evaluation of data that we use in our daily life and represents the futuristic vision of the data that becomes increasingly decentralized and unsupervised

## Features 

* 1024x1024 Resolution
* 20 Seconds
* 20mb/s Bitrate
